  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took the train down during the day to the southern island, where we, where we were waiting that-- and that night were told that, that they were not able to arrange for a boat that night.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as the evening went on, I believe this friend of my uncle's knew a farmer, and they took us out to this farm where we stayed overnight that night.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on this farm, they were going to have the big hunt of the year was starting the next day, so they were having a lot of company.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I vividly remember sleeping in the same bed as my cousin and my parents, and my aunt and uncle slept in the same room, and, and each-- with the two of them in twin beds.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not quite the way they were used, used to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were lucky that somebody was nice enough to have us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the next day, we again were picked up by cabs and taken to a forest, where we were promised there would be a boat at night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, and we waited in this forest near the water all evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then no boat materialized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at the end, there was a children's summer camp, and they broke into the camp and put us down on the springs and the beds and covered us up with their coats, so the grown-ups were freezing all night, distraught about not hearing any boat.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next day, we then were picked up again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and all of these pick-ups, by then we were-- a lot of other people had joined us, and we were probably 20.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other people were not people we knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
